    dc:description "FIG. 4. — Dayus lamellatus Qin & Zhang, 2007: A, head and thorax, dorsal view; B, face; C, male pygofer, lateral view; D, aedeagus and connective, lateral view; E, aedeagus and connective,ventral view;F, male abdominal apodemes of third tergite (upper) and 8th sternite (lower);G, style; H, male pygofer internal process; I, subgenital plate, ventral view; J, male anal tube process, lateral view. Reproduced from Qin & Zhang (2007, figs 22-29), with permission from copyright holder." ;
